This module implements bit operations.

Compile Options:

OptionDescriptionDefault
-d:pon2.bmi=<int>BMI level. (2: BMI2, 1: BMI1, 0: None)2
-d:pon2.clmul=<bool>Uses CLMUL.true

Imports

arrayutils, assign, staticfor

Types

PextMask[T] = T
Mask used in pext.
